00:02:46.948 --> 00:02:48.882
cross reference at the end of the experiment.

00:02:48.882 --> 00:02:51.643
With that out of the way it came down to brute force science.

00:02:51.643 --> 00:02:54.576
Over the course of three months I applied colognes randomly

00:02:54.576 --> 00:02:56.710
